data.description: Welcome to 18300 Nightingale, a charming home nestled on a tranquil 2.43-acres in the private neighborhood of Whispering Pines. This trad-style residence offers a serene living environment, blending privacy & natural beauty seamlessly. Step inside to discover a spacious living area & an upstairs game room/flex room w/new carpeting, ideal for entertaining. The warm & inviting interior complements the expansive exterior, surrounded by wooded landscapes & rolling terrain, creating a picturesque setting. Covered storage for a camper, storage & a pole barn/hobby shop, catering to your all your needs. The property offers a unique blend of privacy & convenience, while the charming traditional arch. style adds character & timeless appeal. Enjoy easy commuting & transportation options w/prox. to 242 and 99. Explore the growing area w/multiple shopping and dining opp. Don't miss this opportunity to own a remarkable prop. Schedule a showing today & envision the serene lifestyle that awaits you.
